&lt;h2 id=&quot;enough-is-enough&quot;&gt;Enough is enough&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It’s tempting to go further, but these web pages do get very big with all these GIFs. But just one more… I quite like this one, the &lt;em&gt;hexadecachoron&lt;/em&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

