&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately you’ve got the imprecise finish &lt;em&gt;without&lt;/em&gt; the reassuring and lovable hand-made quirks. Like those imitation hand-writing fonts, it’s presenting the illusion of manual labour.&lt;/p&gt;

